A state inside state/state of inner chaining
===========================================
Each and every things exists in the form of stream of mass/waves/energy..so on.
Since at extreme state of streaming our observation its self going towards non existence form ie tens to zero.
So we make a summation of streaming into a state for observation. Since this state is look like static in our observation, we can dig into it.

***state is nothing but the complete streaming in some timestamp***

In the entire universe of creation lives is a small pack of energy.
Each and every state of wave/energy interrelated with each others by their networking system between them. These networks use as a path for transmission of energy from one place to another place or from one form to another form.

***Neither any initial point nor any final point for transmission of waves**

The state of every object/energy have multiple states inside it to keep the object in some state, if any one of inside states collapse/break the chaining of states then the
complete object get transformed into another objects or their state will be changed.

Ex-
Our blood cell have many molecules in some state to maintain some state of blood for survival of life, if you touch electric current then the molecule inside blood cell get changed
in some another state and hence it change the state of blood that not support the life and our life reach to end point.

Similar way our meat,bone,marrow,skin..so on maintain some state for living the lives if any one get changed in different state that not support the life, our state life get
changed.

Our body maintain some state for activity of senses, if state of body is in sleep state our senses vanish in that state.
Our senses maintain some state to keep the mind in some state, ie if our senses transform in such a state they wont take any interest in object then our mind change their state and unable to proceed towards test of the objects.
If we look/smell/touch..something give good feeling then state of mind get changed form stress to non stress state since the base of mind get changed.  

Similar way our observation->realization->understanding..so on maintain some state for their activities.

A small group of humans maintain some state to keep bounded in family, if a member of family will change their state(become robber) the entire family state will be changed.
A society maintain some state by using collection of family.

Similar ways not only the humans/lives but also the object/energy/waves maintain some state to keep the existence of lives/object in some fashion.
Our atmosphere maintain some state for existence of lives on this planet.

The solar planets maintain some state to keep in rotation..

Have you been observe how internal chaining maintain their state for external existence of object/energy.
If any of the chain get changed it affect the entire chaining from bottom to top and the entire object/energy come between the path has been transformed their state
to maintain the stability maximum,.

***Chaining of states into or on surface of object is due to exchange of wave at each and every instance of time***


